OL,3,CMan jailed for murdering ex-wife in
OL,4,C'worst case of domestic violence ever
OL,5,Cseen'
OL,7,FA man has been jailed for life after
OL,8,Fhe stabbed his estranged wife to death
OL,9,Fin "one of the worst cases of domestic
OL,10,Fviolence" a police officer has ever
OL,11,Fseen.
OL,13,FNimalarajah Mathiyadaranam, 47,
OL,14,Fcarried out the "pre-meditated and
OL,15,Ftargeted attack" on his former
OL,16,Fpartner, Nilani Nimalarajah, 44, in
OL,17,Fanger after he had not been invited to
OL,18,Fa family celebration, at the shop
OL,19,Fwhere she worked.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/14
