OL,4,C'worst case of domestic violence ever
OL,5,Cseen'
OL,7,FHe had bought the knife from Asda
OL,8,Fwhich he used with "such ferocity it
OL,9,Fcaused the tip of the knife to be
OL,10,Fbroken off" the court heard.
OL,12,FMathiyadaranam is said to have stashed
OL,13,Fthe knife in a JD Sports bag before he
OL,14,Fgot the bus to Low Cost Food and Wine
OL,15,Fon Stanley Road in Bootle, Liverpool,
OL,16,Fwhere his ex-partner worked, on Friday
OL,17,F20 June 2025.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/14
