OL,3,CMan jailed for murdering ex-wife in
OL,4,C'worst case of domestic violence ever
OL,5,Cseen'
OL,7,FMathiyadaranam then drank whiskey and
OL,8,F"poisoned" himself with a pesticide,
OL,9,Fhaving already been banned from
OL,10,Fcontacting the mum of three due to
OL,11,Fprevious episodes of "violence and
OL,12,Fharassment".
OL,14,FThe couple's 17-year-old daughter was
OL,15,Fupstairs above the shop during the
OL,16,Fincident, and saw a body - which she
OL,17,Flater discovered to be her mother - on
OL,18,Fthe floor. She then escaped to the
OL,19,Fshop next door where she called for
OL,20,Fhelp.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/14
