OL,4,C'worst case of domestic violence ever
OL,5,Cseen'
OL,7,FIn her Victim Impact Statement she
OL,8,Fadded: "My mum was such a strong
OL,9,Fwoman; she would never allow anyone to
OL,10,Fdisrespect our family and would stand
OL,11,Fup for who she loved.
OL,13,F"Her absence is something I feel every
OL,14,Fsingle day. I miss her voice, her
OL,15,Flaugh, and the way she made even the
OL,16,Fhardest days feel manageable. There is
OL,17,Fa constant emptiness in my life that I
OL,18,Fwill ever fully recover from.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
