OL,3,CMan jailed for murdering ex-wife in
OL,4,C'worst case of domestic violence ever
OL,5,Cseen'
OL,7,FHe had previously admitted two charges
OL,8,Fof breaching his restraining order.
OL,10,FOpening the trial, prosecutor Annabel
OL,11,FDarlow KC, told the court
OL,12,FMathiyadaranam acted in anger over not
OL,13,Fbeing invited to a traditional Sri
OL,14,FLankan family celebration recognising
OL,15,Fwhen a girl has her first menstrual
OL,16,Fperiod.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/14
