OL,5,Cseen'
OL,7,FShe told the court on Wednesday 14
OL,8,FJanuary: "Nilani's second daughter had
OL,9,Frecently celebrated this milestone in
OL,10,Fher young life, but the defendant had
OL,11,Fnot been invited to the traditional
OL,12,Fcelebration.
OL,14,F"His reaction was one of the most
OL,15,Fappalling and pre-meditated violence.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/14
