OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F393A1768644804
OL,3,CMan jailed for murdering ex-wife in
OL,4,C'worst case of domestic violence ever
OL,5,Cseen'
OL,7,F"He had become estranged from his
OL,8,Ffamily and, indeed, at the time of the
OL,9,Fkilling was subject to court
OL,10,Frestraining orders, which prohibited,
OL,11,For should have prohibited, him from
OL,12,Fapproaching his elder daughter and
OL,13,FNilani at all.
OL,15,F"Those orders were imposed following
OL,16,Fearlier incidents of violence and
OL,17,Fharassment, committed by this
OL,18,Fdefendant."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/14
