OL,3,CMan jailed for murdering ex-wife in
OL,4,C'worst case of domestic violence ever
OL,5,Cseen'
OL,7,FMs Darlow continued: "It was a
OL,8,Fmerciless, sustained and extremely
OL,9,Fbrutal attack. He stabbed Nilani at
OL,10,Fleast 18 times, deliberately targeting
OL,11,Fthe areas of her chest and her head.
OL,13,F"Indeed, he stabbed her with such
OL,14,Fferocity that it caused the tip of the
OL,15,Fknife to be broken off."
OL,17,FJailing Mathiyadaranam for life with a
OL,18,Fminimum term of 29 years at Liverpool
OL,19,FCrown Court on 16 January, the judge
OL,20,Ftold him it was an "exceptionally
OL,21,Fcruel and brutal murder."
