OL,5,Cseen'
OL,7,FHe added the killer was "controlled,
OL,8,Fpurposeful and matter of fact" during
OL,9,Fthe attack.
OL,11,FDetective Chief Inspector Alan
OL,12,FNuttall, who led the investigation,
OL,13,Fsaid Mathiyadaranam had been "intent
OL,14,Fon killing Nilani... and simply didn't
OL,15,Fcare about the consequences."
OL,17,F"I welcome the sentencing of
OL,18,FMathiyaparanam, who was today handed a
OL,19,Fsignificant prison sentence for the
OL,20,Ftruly shocking murder of his estranged
OL,21,Fwife, Nilani," he said.
