OL,3,CMan jailed for murdering ex-wife in
OL,4,C'worst case of domestic violence ever
OL,5,Cseen'
OL,7,F"This act of domestic violence is one
OL,8,Fof the worst I've seen during my time
OL,9,Fworking at Merseyside Police.
OL,11,F"Mathiyaparanam carried out his pre-
OL,12,Fmeditated and targeted attack when
OL,13,Fthere were plenty of people around, it
OL,14,Fwas rush hour traffic on the street
OL,15,Foutside and lots of witnesses.
OL,17,F"He was clearly intent on killing
OL,18,FNilani on this afternoon and simply
OL,19,Fdidn't care about the consequences.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOU
