OL,3,CMan jailed for murdering ex-wife in
OL,4,C'worst case of domestic violence ever
OL,5,Cseen'
OL,7,F"After being arrested he had to be
OL,8,Ftaken to hospital and was in a
OL,9,Fcritical condition for several weeks
OL,10,Fafter he had ingested an unknown
OL,11,Fsubstance during the incident. He
OL,12,Frecovered and was fit enough to face
OL,13,Fjustice in court.
OL,15,F"Although nothing can bring Nilani
OL,16,Fback, I sincerely hope that the
OL,17,Fsentencing of Mathiyaparanam can bring
OL,18,Fher family and friends some comfort.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
